data.description:
BONUS- NEW SEPTIC SYSTEM! PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! WINE COUNTRY !! Spacious and sprawling!! This home is an income producing transient rental! Investors- a property with alot of space for weddings, events and family reunions. But also,  Perfect family home with private setting that sits back on the property, quiet and secluded. Home is currently being used as a transient rental. Are you looking to enjoy the lake and be close to Geneva- on- the- Lake -makes for a perfect setting to continue the transient rental for additional income or make this your next family home. Open floor concept on the main floor.  Yes there are truly 6 bedrooms and even more space for extra beds. MUST see to take in all the space available!!! 3 car garage AND 2 more outbuildings on the property!  
Call agent with any questions or concerns with showing options. Backyard oasis is set for entertaining and so much more potential!
